      "span_text": "Pharmacological manipulation of the PI3K pathway to promote follicle development has been successfully achieved in mice via promotion of other components of PI3K, e.g. by using 740Y-P [CITATION_1] , and it remains to be seen whether this molecule can be used to promote follicle activation and maintain morphologically normal growth in human ovarian follicles.",
